{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2016/02/traveling-by-car-to-bai-li-huang/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"家庭","path":"/tag/family/"},{"name":"山楂树","path":"/tag/hawthorn/"},{"name":"旅游","path":"/tag/travel/"},{"name":"百里荒","path":"/tag/bailihuang/"},{"name":"自驾","path":"/tag/self-driving/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/79e52c03fed898b9bbfa5a27afd152d3/e737e/PANO_20160213_170300cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/79e52c03fed898b9bbfa5a27afd152d3/e737e/PANO_20160213_170300cover.jpg 800w,\n/static/79e52c03fed898b9bbfa5a27afd152d3/5bb6f/PANO_20160213_170300cover.jpg 1600w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/79e52c03fed898b9bbfa5a27afd152d3/e7773/PANO_20160213_170300cover.webp 800w,\n/static/79e52c03fed898b9bbfa5a27afd152d3/f2fb1/PANO_20160213_170300cover.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2016/02/traveling-by-car-to-bai-li-huang/","date":"2016-02-13T12:45:37.000Z","excerpt":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=joBkUahLP2g 新年假期，全家自驾去位 … ","title":"自驾游百里荒","content":"<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=joBkUahLP2g</p>\n<p>新年假期，全家自驾去位于宜昌北边的百里荒景区，山下阴天山上在下雨夹雪，上山的路不好走，权当我练车了。</p>\n<p>到景区已经很晚且风大寒冷，迅速爬上一座山头拍了几张照片后就返程下山，没有看到电影《山楂树之恋》取景的那棵山楂树。</p>\n<p>山上的风力发电的风车，近距离可以听见像飞机飞过一样的气流声。</p>\n<p>冬季山上荒芜一片，又正值新年假期，景区没有人收门票且景区内没什么游客，有的也是像我们一样迅速的游览然后下山。</p>\n<p>山顶上有人露营，还有开房车来过夜，晴朗的时候想必可以看见漂亮的星空。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/pp6GcoXkq282\" target=\"_blank\">在Google Map上查看全景&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2016/02/traveling-by-car-to-bai-li-huang/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}